  "description": "<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p959989/\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_shuangyu.gif\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a><br /><p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.hjfile.cn/doc/201602/1a295c8c5b7447debc9e7fa7cb4a03cf.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t《BBC英音模仿秀》是沪江社团的原创口语社刊，主持人对音频进行重点讲解和示范模仿，并对大家递交的口语模仿作品进行一对一的点评哦！</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>今日主持人：<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">苏殷歉 </span></strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>10秒音频： </strong><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p959989\" title=\"点击获得更好的阅读体验\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_video.gif\" /></a></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>模仿文本：</strong></p>\n<div class=\"langs_en\">\n\t<div class=\"langs_en\">\n\t\tFrom being one of the greatest talents that English football has ever produced, he's now <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/potentially\" target=\"_blank\">potentially</a> on the international <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/scrapheap\" target=\"_blank\">scrapheap</a> at the age of just 29.鲁尼，作为英国足球界的众多伟大的天才之一，才29岁的他很可能已经被国际足坛抛弃了。</div>\n\t<div class=\"langs_en\">\n\t\t<p style=\"line-height: 25px;\">\n\t\t\t<strong>语调示意图：</strong></p>\n\t\t<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n\t\t\t<strong><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><a href=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/shetuan/f08f6b22-63ea-4a84-b86e-adb128c17fe0.png\" style=\"color: rgb(16, 113, 181); text-decoration: none;\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"点击查看原图\"><img src=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/shetuan/f08f6b22-63ea-4a84-b86e-adb128c17fe0.png\" style=\"width: 500px; height: 209px;\" /></a></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></strong></p>\n\t</div>\n</div>\n<p>\n\t<strong>重点单词发音讲解：</strong><span style=\"display: none;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 25px;\">potentially&nbsp; [pə'tɛnʃəli]adv. 可能地，潜在地<br />\n\t</span><span style=\"line-height: 25px;\">scrapheap&nbsp; ['skr&aelig;phiːp]n. 被解雇人群</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<a href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/topi